# RabbitMQ — Message broker with management UI

App: rabbitmq

Rabbitmq:
  from image rabbitmq:3-management-alpine
  open to the public on port 15672
  on port 5672 as amqp using tcp
  health check /api/healthchecks/node
  run 1 copy
  set RABBITMQ_DEFAULT_USER to "{{RABBITMQ_USER}}"
  set RABBITMQ_DEFAULT_PASS to "{{RABBITMQ_PASSWORD}}"
  limit cpu to "500m"
  limit memory to "512Mi"
